      "title": "The Agent Brain",
      "description": "This is Dexter's brain. The core agent loop handles task planning, tool selection, and self-validation. Supporting modules manage system prompts, a scratchpad that logs every tool call for debugging, and an executor that orchestrates tool invocations.",
